    • processPayload

      public static int processPayload(I2PAppContext ctx, SSU2Payload.PayloadCallback cb, byte[] payload, int off, int length, boolean isHandshake, RemoteHostId from) throws IOException, DataFormatException, I2NPMessageException
      Incoming payload. Calls the callback for each received block.
      Parameters:
      isHandshake - true for Token Req, Retry, Sess Req, Sess Created; false for Sess Confirmed
      from - for path challenge/response only, may be null
      Returns:
      number of blocks processed
      Throws:
      IOException - on major errors
      DataFormatException - on parsing of individual blocks
      I2NPMessageException - on parsing of I2NP block
